{"tid":1165152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊b又派福利！！ 條腿正到呢！","createTime":"2019-05-21T15:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T18:39:09.000Z","uid":35864,"like":18,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5bd02a45f508a71262020fb973547113d06cf0ae","tid":1165152,"uid":35864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:05:07.000Z","msg":"游蕙禎又派福利！繼 3 月初在她的 Facebook 專頁上載了穿運動 bra-top 戴著耳機做運動的健康相片，提供耳機優惠之後。最近她又在個人專頁上載相片，揹著瑞典 Gaston Luga 背囊拍照。在專頁上並提供專屬折扣碼：yauwaiching，憑此折扣碼到官網買袋可享 85 折優惠。不過游蕙禎在該帖表示，「官網上面既貨品圖片睇落斯文又細個，實物比我想像中大。」<br />\n<br />\n其實 Gaston Luga  背囊有男款和女款，採用厚實的棉布和人造皮革製成，而且內層有 1 個可放置 13 吋至 15 吋筆記型電腦的夾層，方便帶電腦返工或返學使用。至於有網民的留言則錯做點，留言「人靚怎襯都靚」、「罹拉」、「身材好正，禎禎靚女」，似乎留言的粉絲都將重點放在游蕙禎身上，個袋靚唔靚反而是其次。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wuGXgaT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwuGXgaT.jpg&h=520e7706&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zCQw44e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzCQw44e.jpg&h=97a86c33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HovkYpf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHovkYpf.jpg&h=1579a077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2355269\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F2355269&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6Tf2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=1c0f6991\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/2355269</a>"},{"pid":"e168875a81503d1b5f810a34d82fe7db79dd9560","tid":1165152,"uid":238551,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T15:06:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8710e37525c100206c45a44f945e4eecbca73a1d","tid":11651